becomeAHost.caseStudies.allforclimate-co: En värd för din lokala miljökampanj, vi agerar som ett gemensamt administrativt backoffice så att lokala grupper kan fokusera på sina mål.
becomeAHost.caseStudies.foundation: The Open Collective Platform provides the tools to more effectively manage group finances. They can offer their donors tax-deductible status without needing to incorporate a legal entity.
becomeAHost.caseStudies.opensource: We provide financial and legal infrastructure for thousands of open source projects. We’re an API between the world of distributed collaboration and the world of accounting and invoices.
becomeAHost.caseStudies.socialchangenest: Vi har kunnat stödja över 150 hjälporganisationer att komma igång snabbt genom att förse dem med finansiellt värdskap.
becomeAHost.caseStudies.wwcode: Whenever we start a new meetup chapter, we pair it with an Open Collective so they have the means to raise money under our umbrella.
becomeAHost.description: Open Collective är byggt för att effektivisera processer, minska overhead, öka transparensen, och göra det möjligt för din organisation att samla in och hantera pengar för fler projekt på kortare tid. <learnMoreLink>Lär dig mer</learnMoreLink>.

becomeAHost.joinUsSection.subtitle: Open Collective makes fiscal sponsorship shine. Grantees and project participants will love the simplicity and accessibility, and you’ll love the huge reduction of overheads.
becomeAHost.networks.description: Who want to enable local fundraising while operating a single common legal entity, such as meetups and social movements.
becomeAHost.nonprofits.description: Who want to enable unincorporated projects that further their mission areas to receive grants and donations under their umbrella.
becomeAHost.reduceOverhead.description: When you’re managing funds for multiple projects or groups, it's easy to get overwhelmed by complex spreadsheets and countless email threads. Open Collective automates budget tracking, reporting, expense processing, and payments, making your job a lot easier.

Om ett bidrag eller en kostnad är för ett företag, använd då en organisationsprofil så att rätt faktureringsinformation finns på kvitton och fakturor. Organisationer kan också utfärda presentkort.

fiscalHosting.companiesGivingBack.descri: Kan samarbeta med en idell finansiell värd för att separera komersiell aktivitet från ideell aktivitet och för att koordinera stöd och sponsring.
fiscalHosting.crowdFunding.description: Seeking a place to hold the money and a way to offer accountability to their backers.
fiscalHosting.description: Tänk på din gemenskap, projekt eller initiativ som en planta, och en finansiell värd som en blomstrande trädgård. Värden skapar en miljö där din unika buske, vinranka, eller träd kan bli vattnade, växa och blomma.
fiscalHosting.distributeCollaboration.de: Like an open source software project, which isn’t owned by anyone and wants resources held in common.
fiscalHosting.feature.acceptAndSpendFund: Det går oftast fort att godkännas av värden och kunna börja ta emot och betala ut pengar. Jämfört med att starta em egen förening eller stiftelse är det väldigt snabbt och smidigt att använda en finansiell värd.
fiscalHosting.feature.automaticReporting: No need to spend hours creating reports for funders. The Open Collective platform has automated quantitative reporting built in. Just sent the funder a link to your page! There are great tools for qualitative reporting too, like posting blogs and newsletters, which also serve to keep your wider community engaged and up to date.
fiscalHosting.feature.networkingAndSolid: En värd bör vara en gemenskap av projekt med någonting gemensamt. De kan tillhandahålla tjänster till samhället som helhet och möjliggöra kopplingar mellan projekt. En värd blir mer än summan av sina delar.
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance: Organize your finances, all in one place
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance.de: No more messy spreadsheets! Income from credit card transactions, bank transfers, PayPal, even ticket sales, grants, and sponsorships are all tracked automatically in one transparent budget. With a robust yet user-friendly system for submitting and approving expenses, tracking outgoing funds is a breeze, too.
fiscalHosting.feature.organizeFinance.ta: Er ekonomi på ett och samma ställe
fiscalHosting.feature.sustainabilityDesi: Om ditt projekt inte har ett slutdatum bör inte din finansiering ta slut. En vanlig crowdfunding-kampanj tar slut. Stöd finansierar bara verksamheten tills de tar slut. Finansiellt värdskap möjliggör att kombinera olika strömmar av återkommande donationer hjälper dig att bygga långvariga relationer.
fiscalHosting.fees.description: Värdar tar ofta ut en avgift för den tjänst de tillhandahåller. Vissa värdar håller avgifterna låga och erbjuder enklare tjänster, medan andra har högre avgifter och ger mer. Vissa värdar tar inte ut avgifter alls.

OCFHostApplication.faq.missionImpact.con: Increasing access to educational resources and training: With the advance of technology and the movement towards a society where people work together to enhance and develop the future, there has been an increase in the number of organizations and groups that are coming together to promote education. {lineBreak}{lineBreak} Creating a positive social impact: Sponsor’s social impact purpose is aimed at finding ways to (i) eliminate prejudice and discrimination; (ii) combat community deterioration; (iii) decrease juvenile delinquency; (iv) serve the less fortunate or distressed; (v) serve to prevent animal or child cruelty; or (vi) create a positive impact on society. {lineBreak}{lineBreak} Developing tools to improve civic participation within cities or communities: Sponsor host projects aimed at fostering civic participation, democratic debate and rebuilding community ties and strengths.

OCFHostApplication.howItWorks.list: • Donations are made to our 501(c)(3) (tax-exempt status applies){lineBreak} • We make a “grant” to your group/project{lineBreak} • We send donors their receipts, disburse funds/reimburse expenses after your approval, send out the tax forms to independent contractors as applicable{lineBreak} • You have complete access to collect, spend, manage your money on our platform.
OCFHostApplication.importance: It can take years for a group to get 501(c)(3) non-profit status. Fiscal hosts are especially helpful to newly formed nonprofit groups, large and small. We act as a legal entity for your group, organizing the back-end of your fundraising efforts. It’s fast and easy to apply. Once your group is approved, you can begin collecting funds immediately.
